          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Veterans Affairs Purchase Card Misuse Mitigation Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to prohibit employees who have knowingly misused VA purchase cards from serving as purchase card holders or approving officials. </p> <p>Such prohibition shall be in addition to any other applicable penalty.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-08T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
        <item>
